videos.headline: UNLV's Thomas takes it 71 yards to the house vs. USC
videos.description: Lexington Thomas takes the ball 71 yards for a UNLV touchdown to take the lead over #15 USC.

videos.headline: UNLV's Rogers threads the needle for a TD
videos.description: Armani Rogers finds Kendal Keys in the second quarter for a 29-yard touchdown, extending UNLV's lead over USC.

videos.headline: Malepeai runs through traffic for USC TD
videos.description: USC's Vavae Malepeai runs the ball two yards late in the second quarter to retake the lead.

videos.headline: JT Daniels tosses his first collegiate TD
videos.description: JT Daniels finds Amon-Ra St. Brown at the beginning of the 4th quarter to extend USC's lead.

videos.headline: Ware takes it to the house
videos.description: Aca'Cedric Ware runs the ball for a 15-yard Trojan touchdown.

videos.headline: UNLV's Rogers finds Fauolo for TD
videos.description: Armani Rogers finds Giovanni Fauolo for the 5-yard touchdown to shorten UNLV's deficit.

videos.headline: Malepeai runs untouched into the end zone
videos.description: Vavae Malepeai runs 20 yards untouched late in the 4th quarter for a USC touchdown.
